{"word":"H4541 - מַסֵּכָה - maççêkâh - mas-say-kaw' - Covering","slug":"H4541","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַסֵּכָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>maççêkâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mas-say-kaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Covering"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E1;&#x05BC;&#x05DB;&#x05D4; - masse&#x0302;ka&#x0302;h</b> - <i>mas-say-kaw'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5258\">H5258</a>; properly a <i>pouring</i> over, that is, <i>fusion</i> of metal (especially a <i>cast</i> image); by implication a <i>libation</i>, that is, league; concretely a <i>coverlet</i> (as if <i>poured</i> out): - covering, molten (image), vail."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4545\">H4545</a>, <a href=\"#/H5259\">H5259</a>"}]}